Video footage of a road rage incident that took place in Durban recently has been spread on social media.The footage shows a motorist assaulting a taxi driver&#8230; with the motorist continueing to shout, &#8220;Do you think you own the road!?&#8221;Onlookers at the scene of the incident do nothing but take a look at the &#8216;action&#8217;. And some video the ordeal&#8230; because this is the era of video recording everything we do&#8230; both good and bad.